Photo Frame 1.0 showcases images in new style using jQuery. The main intention is to have a set of rotated thumbnails that,

Once clicked, animate to form the selected image. You can navigate through the images with previous and next buttons and

When the big image gets clicked it will scatter across the screen to form a Grid layout of images. Basically here the images are shown from Users Facebook profile via Albums.

Technologies: PHP 5.4.3, html 5.

Plugins: jQuery 1.8.2, jQuery UI 1.9.2,Facebook-PHP-SDK v3.2.3, Twitter-bootstrap v2.3.2,NailThumb v1.1.
